name: Bent #3
description:
A collection of colourful geometries inspired by hard-edge paintings from the 1960s.


Each 1/1 of 5 in this series has been curated from the output of a generative algorithm that determined the colour palette, colour sequence, number of stripes and number of bends.

 Made with code and love by AutoEclectus.

 AutoEclectus is a visual artist specialising in code-based generative works.
